                                    <h3 class="epsilon padding-bottom20"><a href="news/noaa-will-curb-illegal-fishing/index.html">NOAA to Congress: We will curb illegal, unreported and unregulated fishing</a></h3>
                                    
                                    <p class="article">Illegal fishing is a global problem that threatens marine habitats, food security, and the economic viability of nations, leading annual losses  between $10 billion to $23 billion. This issue calls for satellite-based AIS applications that can track and monitor a vessel’s location and help improve the world's oceans.</p>
