                                    <h3 class="epsilon padding-bottom20"><a href="news/noaa-announces-will-likely-buy-weather-data/index.html">NOAA announces that it will likely buy weather data if it’s available</a></h3>
                                    
                                    <p class="article">Old satellites cause government agencies, like NOAA, to fill the weather data gap with information from private companies specializing in cubesats. This highlights the need for Spire's unique weather forecasting application (Spire Stratos&trade;) to provide fresh monitoring, reporting, and analysis. </p>
